Workflow:

**** make changes in rtm_tcr_unittest.user.js
 - test in rtm.tcr.unittest account; mainly in Chrome, then in Firefox, Safari

Chrome:

cp rtm_tcr_unittest.user.js ~/Library/Application\ Support/Google/Chrome/Default/Extensions/leaegfagppffnlnfjambidbohijokkbe/1.0_0/script.js

* disable, reenable extension; reload RTM page

Firefox:

cp rtm_tcr_unittest.user.js ~/Library/Application\ Support/Firefox/Profiles/gh6uxe30.default/gm_scripts/RTM_Tag_Cloud_Restructurer_\(rtm.tcr.unittest\)/rtm_tcr_unittest.user.js


**** diff/patch rtm_tcr_unittest.user.js to rtm_tcr.user.js

diff -u rtm_tcr_unittest.user.js rtm_tcr.user.js > rtm_tcr_unittest_to_general.diff

* modify diff so changes only Greasemonkey context, section dictionary

patch -u -i rtm_tcr_unittest_to_general.diff rtm_tcr_unittest.user.js -o rtm_tcr.user.js


**** diff/patch rtm_tcr.user.js to rtm_tcr_emalminator.user.js

diff -u rtm_tcr.user.js rtm_tcr_emalminator.user.js > rtm_tcr_general_to_em.diff

* maintain diff so changes only Greasemonkey context, section dictionary (if necessary)


patch -u -i rtm_tcr_general_to_em.diff rtm_tcr.user.js -o rtm_tcr_emalminator.user.js

* once emalminator script patched, test on personal account

Chrome:

cp rtm_tcr_emalminator.user.js ~/Library/Application\ Support/Google/Chrome/Default/Extensions/njklpkmfebgooabmbjdhpadmohnbeomc/1.0_0/script.js


Firefox:

cp rtm_tcr_emalminator.user.js ~/Library/Application\ Support/Firefox/Profiles/gh6uxe30.default/gm_scripts/RTM_Tag_Cloud_Restructurer_\(emalminator\)/rtm_tcr_emalminator.user.js


**** diff/patch rtm_tcr.user.js to rtm_tcr_example.user.js

diff -u rtm_tcr.user.js rtm_tcr_example.user.js > rtm_tcr_general_to_example.diff

* maintain diff so changes only Greasemonkey context, section dictionary

patch -u -i rtm_tcr_general_to_example.diff rtm_tcr.user.js -o rtm_tcr_example.user.js

* once example script patched, test on example account, generate documentation

Chrome:

cp rtm_tcr_example.user.js ~/Library/Application\ Support/Google/Chrome/Default/Extensions/flblipakiocabbhjadegchbollinjjmk/1.0_0/script.js


Firefox:

cp rtm_tcr_example.user.js ~/Library/Application\ Support/Firefox/Profiles/gh6uxe30.default/gm_scripts/RTM_Tag_Cloud_Restructurer_\(rtm.tcr.example\)/rtm_tcr_example.user.js







